<s> Just a brief reminder that we're in the final days of a working group last call for comments period on the WebDAV Ordered Collections protocol, draft-ietf-webdav-ordering-protocol-07.  </s>
<s> From the abstract of the -07 specification  </s>
<s> This specification extends the WebDAV Distributed Authoring Protocol  </s>
<s> to support server-side ordering of collection members.  </s>
<s> Of particular  </s>
<s> interest are orderings that are not based on property values, and so  </s>
<s> cannot be achieved using a search protocol's ordering option and cannot be maintained automatically by the server.  </s>
<s> Protocol elements  </s>
<s> are defined to let clients specify the position in the ordering of each collection member, as well as the semantics governing the  </s>
<s> ordering.  </s>
<s> This last call for comments period ends Sunday, April 27, 2003, at midnight, US Pacific time.  </s>
